raph -->\n<p>Yes.  In order to protect you from false accusations, Janitorial Service Bonds do to pay claims unless the employee was convicted of the theft by a court of proper jurisdiction. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"row px-4 py-5 ez-light\"} -->\n<div id=\"glossary\" class=\"wp-block-group row px-4 py-5 ez-light\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Bond Glossary</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>First fact about bond yada yada?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The actual fact text that will show about this yada yada. The actual fact text that will show about this yada yada. The actual fact text that will show about this yada yada. The actual fact text that will show about this yada yada. The actual fact text that will show about this yada yada. The actual fact text that will show about this yada yada.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>First fact about bond yada yada?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The actual fact text that will show about this yada yada. The actual fact text that will show about this yada yada. The actual fact text that will show about this yada yada. The actual fact text that will show about this yada yada. The actual fact text that will show about this yada yada. The actual fact text that will show about this yada yada.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"p-4 p-lg-5 mt-5 mb-5 bg-light ms-5-lg me-5-lg rounded-3\"} -->\n<div id=\"contact\" class=\"wp-block-group p-4 p-lg-5 mt-5 mb-5 bg-light ms-5-lg me-5-lg rounded-3\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Ask Us A Question</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:wpforms/form-selector {\"formId\":\"11\"} /--></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Front Page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '',